    <dashboard enable-sort-zone-taborder='true' name='Projected'>
      <style />
      <size sizing-mode='automatic' />
      <zones>
        <zone h='100000' id='4' type-v2='layout-basic' w='100000' x='0' y='0'>
          <zone h='98222' id='8' param='horz' type-v2='layout-flow' w='98882' x='559' y='889'>
            <zone h='98222' id='6' type-v2='layout-basic' w='81284' x='559' y='889'>
              <zone forceUpdate='true' h='35889' id='3' type-v2='text' w='62150' x='559' y='63222'>
                <formatted-text>
                  <run bold='true' fontalignment='1' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='20'>THE HARD TRUTH</run>
                  <run fontalignment='1'>Æ&#10;</run>
                  <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                  <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12' italic='true'>Ireland&apos;s current 11.6% forest cover is the third-lowest in Europe. The government&apos;s Afforestation Scheme commits to 8,000 hectares of new planting per year — but at this rate, the 18% target won&apos;t be reached until approximately 2077.</run>
                  <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
                  <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12' italic='true'>WHY THIS MATTERS</run>
                  <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                  <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12' italic='true'>- The 2027 deadline is mathematically impossible at 8,000 ha/year</run>
                  <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                  <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12' italic='true'>- Each year of under-planting compounds into decades of delay</run>
                  <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                  <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12' italic='true'>- Climate commitments under EU LULUCF depend on meeting this target</run>
                  <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
                  <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12' italic='true'>THE DASHED LINE at 18% is the national goal. </run>
                  <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                  <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12' italic='true'>Notice how many decades beyond 2027 the orange line takes to meet it.</run>
                </formatted-text>
                <zone-style>
                  <format attr='border-color' value='#000000' />
                  <format attr='border-style' value='none' />
                  <format attr='border-width' value='0' />
                  <format attr='margin' value='4' />
                </zone-style>
              </zone>
              <zone h='62333' id='5' name='Projected Forest Cover' w='81284' x='559' y='889'>
                <zone-style>
                  <format attr='border-color' value='#000000' />
                  <format attr='border-style' value='none' />
                  <format attr='border-width' value='0' />
                  <format attr='margin' value='4' />
                </zone-style>
              </zone>
              <zone forceUpdate='true' h='35889' id='10' type-v2='text' w='19134' x='62709' y='63222'>
                <formatted-text>
                  <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12' italic='true'>WHAT THIS CHART SHOWS</run>
                  <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                  <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12' italic='true'>The coloured line traces projected forest cover year-on-year:</run>
                  <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
                  <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12' italic='true'>- Pink (Baseline) = pre-scheme period</run>
                  <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
                  <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12' italic='true'>- Teal (Scheme Active) = 2023–2027 government programme</run>
                  <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
                  <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12' italic='true'>- Orange (Post-Scheme) = continuation at same rate</run>
                  <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
                  <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12' italic='true'>- Green/Yellow dots = target approached / reached</run>
                  <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                </formatted-text>
                <zone-style>
                  <format attr='border-color' value='#000000' />
                  <format attr='border-style' value='none' />
                  <format attr='border-width' value='0' />
                  <format attr='margin' value='4' />
                </zone-style>
              </zone>
            </zone>
            <zone fixed-size='252' h='98222' id='7' is-fixed='true' param='vert' type-v2='layout-flow' w='17598' x='81843' y='889'>
              <zone h='16222' id='9' name='Projected Forest Cover' pane-specification-id='0' param='[federated.0ap8dgu1klo5mz1cte1r103q7dvb].[none:Scheme_Status:nk]' type-v2='color' w='17598' x='81843' y='889'>
                <zone-style>
                  <format attr='border-color' value='#000000' />
                  <format attr='border-style' value='none' />
                  <format attr='border-width' value='0' />
                  <format attr='margin' value='4' />
                </zone-style>
              </zone>
            </zone>
          </zone>
          <zone-style>
            <format attr='border-color' value='#000000' />
            <format attr='border-style' value='none' />
            <format attr='border-width' value='0' />
            <format attr='margin' value='8' />
          </zone-style>
        </zone>
      </zones>
