                <formatted-text>
                  <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='15' italic='true'>Ireland&apos;s Afforestation Scheme (2023–2027) targets 18% forest cover via 8,000 ha/year planting. At this rate, the 18% target is mathematically reached around 2077 — over 50 years late. This DSS allows scenario modelling of alternative planting rates.&quot;</run>
